{"article_id":"mBDDmFS1HjdQsDgL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"While Congress passed a massive $ 1.3 trillion omnibus spending bill early Friday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump threatened to veto it later in the morning ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"meaning a government shutdown is still a possibility .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The president pointed to the legislation ' s lack of full funding for his border wall between the United States and Mexico","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"and that there are no protections for recipients of the Obama-era Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"\" I am considering a VETO of the Omnibus Spending Bill","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"based on the fact","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that the 800,000 plus DACA recipients have been totally abandoned by the Democrats","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"( not even mentioned in Bill )","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and the BORDER WALL ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"which is desperately needed for our National Defense ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"is not fully funded , \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he wrote .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"I am considering a VETO of the Omnibus Spending Bill","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"based on the fact","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that the 800,000 plus DACA recipients have been totally abandoned by the Democrats","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"( not even mentioned in Bill )","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and the BORDER WALL ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"which is desperately needed for our National Defense ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"is not fully funded .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"March 23 , 2018","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"Earlier Friday Trump alluded to his frustration over these issues","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"but did not mention it in relation to the spending bill .","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"\" DACA was abandoned by the Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Very unfair to them !","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Would have been tied to desperately needed Wall , \"","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"he wrote .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"DACA was abandoned by the Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Very unfair to them !","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Would have been tied to desperately needed Wall .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"March 23 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Many Republican lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"unhappy with the fiscal burden","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"the bill places on our nation ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"were pleased with the news ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"encouraging him to do so .","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"`` Please do , Mr. President .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"I am just down the street","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and will bring you a pen .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The spending levels","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"without any offsets","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"are grotesque ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"throwing all of our children under the bus .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Totally irresponsible , ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Sen. Bob Corker tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Please do , Mr. President .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"I am just down the street","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and will bring you a pen .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The spending levels","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"without any offsets","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"are grotesque ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"throwing all of our children under the bus .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Totally irresponsible .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"https : //t.co/np7BmP1AkB","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"- Senator Bob Corker","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"( @ SenBobCorker )","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"March 23 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"`` I a